ProMED

[The black-faced spoonbill (_Platalea minor_) is an endangered wading bird. It has a very restricted distribution, confined to coastal areas of eastern Asia. For a picture of this beautiful bird go to https://www.naturepl.com/cache/pcache2/01670497.jpg. - Mod.PMB

